data.description: No HOA!!! This beautiful 4-bed 3-bath gem is fully turnkey and situated on a large corner lot.  Double ensuite split floorplan with new roof (2022), new HVAC (2023), new kitchen appliances (2023), new outdoor ceiling fans (2023), air purification system, and tankless water heater. Granite countertops in kitchen, master and guest bath. Ceramic tile throughout the main house, laminate in the bedrooms. Freshly painted interior and exterior of house.  Privacy fenced in backyard and beautiful built in pool with salt system. Large storage shed with electricity in backyard. Hurricane-proof impact windows and doors, as well as energy conservation screens on front and east-facing windows. Conveniently located near Downtown West Palm Beach, Palm Beach Outlets, Palm Beach International Airport and Palm Beach Island.
